        <section id="design-section">
            <article id="startups" class="flex-inl article-container dsn-art active-dsn-art">
                <div class="left-side-label-cont">
                    <span class="left-side-label">&nbsp;</span>
                </div>
                <div class="article-img-cont">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300/?text=Test+Article" alt="Article Img">
                </div>
                <div class="vr-lg"></div>
                <div class="article-content">
                    <div class="article-title-cont">
                        <h3 class="article-title">So, you have an Idea...</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="article-body-cont">
                        <p class="article-body">
                            ... But you know you suck at designing things in Photoshop; last thing you drew in the 
                            back of your high school notebook was "Cool S"; and you have the design aesthetic of
                            a toddler's drawing on the family fridge. We get it. Our graphic designers will make
                            your design visions pop!
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="right-side-label-cont">
                    <span class="right-side-label">Not a Startup Company?</span>
                </div>
            </article>
            <article id="small-biz" class="flex-inl article-container dsn-art">
                <div class="left-side-label-cont">
                    <span class="left-side-label">"Maybe I am a startup..."</span>
                </div>
                <div class="article-img-cont">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300/?text=Test+Article" alt="Article Img">
                </div>
                <div class="vr-lg"></div>
                <div class="article-content">
                    <div class="article-title-cont">
                        <h3 class="article-title">Hey! You already have a brand!</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="article-body-cont">
                        <p class="article-body">
                            That's awesome, you know.. But, Boomers Inc. designed your brand in MS Word and Paint,
                            and now you feel obligated to keep using clipart as your business logo. Yeesh... Pretty
                            2010s if you ask us. You can do better than that! Not to fear! We'll take your existing
                            designs and make them look something more... <i>this Century</i>? We'll bring your design
                            out of Windows XP, and at least teach you to use Windows 10... Like the rest of us. Don't
                            worry... We'll keep your brand aesthetic true to what Good Ol' Grandpappy who founded the
                            company passed on to ya.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="right-side-label-cont">
                    <span class="right-side-label">"Actually, we've got something good already."</span>
                </div>
            </article>
            <article id="sme-biz" class="flex-inl article-container dsn-art">
                <div class="left-side-label-cont">
                    <span class="left-side-label">"My brand probably can get some touch ups..."</span>
                </div>
                <div class="article-img-cont">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300/?text=Test+Article" alt="Article Img">
                </div>
                <div class="vr-lg"></div>
                <div class="article-content">
                    <div class="article-title-cont">
                        <h3 class="article-title">Dang! Looking snazzy!</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="article-body-cont">
                        <p class="article-body">
                            Man... It must have taken you months of design research to come up with this. But, have
                            you considered more creative ways to show-off your already awesome looking brand? No?
                            Oh-.. You can't because <b><i>Overpriced Marketing Designs Inc.</i></b> locked you in a
                            pretty locked down contract? Well, while we can't get you out of that bad deal you got
                            into, we can definitely take over when you finally tell them to kick the can; and given
                            you actually bought the rights to your design<sup>(?)</sup>, we can blow you up, bigger
                            than ol' <b><i>MoneyJim & Co.</i></b> over there, at a better price too!
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="right-side-label-cont">
                    <span class="right-side-label">&nbsp;</span>
                </div>
            </article>
        </section>
        <section id="design-cta-section">
            <button>I'm Design Interested!</button>
            <p>Well? You've read the button. Are you? Well; click it! Or see how we can help you...</p>
