                </div>
            </article>
            <article id="cut-through" class="flex-inl article-container dsn-art">
                <div class="article-content">
                    <div class="article-title-cont">
                        <h3 class="article-title">Hey! You already have a brand!</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="article-body-cont">
                        <p class="article-body">
                            That's awesome, you know.. But, Boomers Inc. designed your brand in MS Word and Paint,
                            and now you feel obligated to keep using clipart as your business logo. Yeesh... Pretty
                            2010s if you ask us. You can do better than that! Not to fear! We'll take your existing
                            designs and make them look something more... <i>this Century</i>? We'll bring your design
                            out of Windows XP, and at least teach you to use Windows 10... Like the rest of us. Don't
                            worry... We'll keep your brand aesthetic true to what Good Ol' Grandpappy who founded the
                            company passed on to ya.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="vr-lg"></div>
                <div class="article-img-cont">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300/?text=Test+Article" alt="Article Img">
                </div>
            </article>
